| Comment: Hunt 1 — Credential path reads from telemetry
index=main sourcetype=openclaw_telemetry event_type="tool_executed"
| where tool_name="file_read"
| where match(tool_path, "\.ssh|\.aws|\.moltbot|\.clawdbot|id_rsa|id_ed25519|\.bak|credentials")
| table _time host user session_id tool_name tool_path
| sort - _time

| Comment: Hunt 2 — Off-hours high-risk tool execution (uncomment to run)
`comment("
index=main sourcetype=openclaw_telemetry event_type=tool_executed
| eval hour=strftime(_time, "%H")
| eval day_of_week=strftime(_time, "%u")
| where (hour < "08" OR hour >= "19") OR (day_of_week >= "6")
| where tool_name IN ("exec", "shell", "python_repl", "email_send", "browser_action")
| table _time host user session_id tool_name hour day_of_week
")`

| Comment: Hunt 3 — Burst execution (>10 tool calls per session per minute)
`comment("
index=main sourcetype=openclaw_telemetry event_type=tool_executed
| bin _time span=1m
| stats count as tool_calls, values(tool_name) as tools_used
    by _time session_id host
| where tool_calls > 10
| sort - tool_calls
")`
